---
title: Easy Turkey Cottage Pie with Cheesy Cheddar Mashed Potatoes
description: This classic casserole combines saucy turkey filling with extra cheesy cheddar mashed potatoes. Broiling for the last few minutes gives this cottage pie a delicious golden crust.
